Copy secret-dist.php to secret.php to start blogging.
For making it nicely working, you should configure $context_root and $your_tz
properly at least. 

License of usage:
  For using ESiBlog itself, there's no restriction.
  But when using for commercial purpose, you may want to consult license
  or developer of other projects listed below for restrictions, 
  especially for Responsive Filemanager.
  
Other projects ESiBlog is using:
 * GeSHi - Generic Syntax Highlighter -- http://qbnz.com/highlighter/
 * TinyMCE -- http://www.tinymce.com/
 * Responsive Filemanager -- http://www.responsivefilemanager.com/